<module>
    <h>mi</h>
    <p><g>mi</g>
        <en>I, me</en> is the first person singular <a href="?xx=nouns/personal_pronouns">personal
            pronoun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <section id="verbs-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <!--<p><g>mi</g> can be used as the subject of a verb.</p>-->
            <p>Examples with the predicative verb <g href="?gd=bi">bi</g>
                <en>be</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha mi trang an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>I am busy today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9 [226]</ref>
                    </li>
                    <!--<li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>mi</m> fuar agus tha <m>mi</m> sgìth.</gd>
                        <tr>I am cold and I am tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>-->
                    <li>
                        <gd>Nach eil thu sgìth? Tha, tha mi glé sgìth.</gd>
                        <tr>Aren’t you tired. Yes, I am very tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                    <!--<li>
                        <gd>Ciamar a tha sibh? Tha mi gu math, tapadh leibh.</gd>
                        <tr>How are you? I am well, thank you.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 15</ref>
                    </li>-->
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil thu a’ fuireach? Tha mi a’ fuireach anns a’
                            chlachan.</gd>
                        <tr>Where do you live? I live in the village.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                    <!--<li>
                        <gd>Bha mi anns a’ mhonadh an dé. Chunnaic mi caoraich agus crodh anns a’
                            mhonadh.</gd>
                        <tr>I was on the moor yesterday. I saw sheep and cattle on the moor.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21</ref>
                    </li>-->
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with other verbs – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd><a href="?gd=faic">Chunnaic</a> mi cù aig an dorus.</gd>
                        <tr>I saw a dog at the door.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Bha mi anns a’ mhonadh an dé. Chunnaic mi caoraich agus crodh anns a’
                            mhonadh.</gd>
                        <tr>I was on the moor yesterday. I saw sheep and cattle on the moor.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>


